  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "25f533d6b58b64ec510991eba474ae256f6af7262bb2d22ff9a404eca1d6d205": "I will not forget what you did for my family [?]. Those 500,000 coins have allowed us to put food on the table.",
    "335fe69c3c6b346938449988c6efc11032d7ce6be21880721b859f2e0768c644": "I'm sorry for lying to you [?], it was just all part of the ploy to make our family seem wealthy.",
    "47f72739a1116dd0f43d814c9548ff0c6e64de5089d1c671527ae7a63ab41175": "I will not forget what you did for my family, [?]. Those 500,000 coins have allowed us to put food on the table.",
    "80fa1e11b214382586239a50bdfe4f6ba3a6f2eb30ffe044499e285177dc1102": "That is excellent news [?]. It's good to hear they are doing well.",
    "9df8ee86353cb83789fe26d86d6c3093896d71453a3dcd79d4b6e7e7839a7f3e": "I'm sorry for lying to you, [?], it was just all part of the ploy to make our family seem wealthy.",
    "dd88fa025acff5572b2204b0cca22b691c83d5f0f360e9256081dbf1d18c6327": "Our family just pretends to be rich [?]. We gave ourselves a fancy surname, pretended the gauntlets are a family heirloom and asked adventurers to solve our family issues."
